Innovation and Culture Center

The firm headquarters of "Vertex Arquitectura" embodies the hybrid design of a monument and self-sustaining structure among a field of underused and abandoned industrial structures. The proposal melds the evolving artistic and cultural scene of Lubbock and its legendary, almost forgotten status as the Hub City of West Texas.
